---
title: Pork Steaks and Mustard Chive Sauce with Roast Potatoes, Honeyed Carrots and Radishes
description: This delicious Pork Steaks and Mustard Chive Sauce has been expertly designed by our chefs as a lighter option to help with a balanced lifestyle.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-steaks-and-mustard-chive-sauce-989932c8-18e23aca.jpg
